OL,3,CSt Helier Deputies confirmed after
OL,4,Cvote recount
OL,6,FDeputy-elect Lee Carpenter has had his
OL,7,Fseat confirmed after a recount in St
OL,8,FHelier Central.
OL,10,FIt was triggered after the first
OL,11,Fresult revealed just 21 votes between
OL,12,Fthe elected Reform Jersey politician
OL,13,Fand unsuccessful independent candidate
OL,14,FRobin Ward, within the official 1%
OL,15,Fmargin of error.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/4
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
