OL,3,CSt Helier Deputies confirmed after
OL,4,Cvote recount
OL,6,FFollowing a full recount for the
OL,7,Fdistrict's four Deputy spots, only one
OL,8,Fvote was "discovered to be mis-
OL,9,Fattributed" - sixth-placed candidate
OL,10,FClaire De Than gained one and Mr Ward
OL,11,Flost one - which did not affect the
OL,12,Ffinal order.
OL,14,FThe recount took place at St Helier
OL,15,FParish Hall from 10am on Wednesday (10
OL,16,FJune), with the confirmed result
OL,17,Fannounced around lunchtime.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/4
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
