OL,3,CSt Helier Deputies confirmed after
OL,4,Cvote recount
OL,6,FIt means Mr Carpenter, Carina Alves,
OL,7,FLyndsay Feltham and Catherine Curtis
OL,8,Fwill be sworn into their new positions
OL,9,Fon Friday (12 June), alongside the
OL,10,Frest of the Assembly.
OL,12,FThe final results for the St Helier
OL,13,FCentral Deputy race are as follows:
OL,15,FNOT ELECTED
